pan></figcaption></figure><p>The \u2018McGurk effect\u2019 could take you down a YouTube rabbit hole.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.popsci.com/health", "link": "https://www.popsci.com/health/mcgurk-effect", "date_published": "2023-10-26T13:00:00+00:00", "bookmarked": false, "dead": null, "artist": "Popular Science", "album": "Popular Science", "user": null, "language": "en-US", "thumbnail": "https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2021/04/28/cropped-PSC3.png?auto=webp&width=32&height=32"}, {"source": "https://www.popsci.com/feed", "title": "Save 60% on Blink Mini security cameras during Amazon\u2019s early Black Friday sale", "description": "<figure class=\"Article-thumbnail orgnc-SingleImage orgnc-SingleImage--center orgnc-SingleImage--hasCaption\">\n                    <div class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-wrapper\"><img alt=\"Blink Amazon Deals\" class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-image webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"936\" src=\"https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2023/10/26/Blink-Amazon-Deals.jpg?auto=webp&amp;width=1440&amp;height=936\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1440\" /></div><figcaption class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-caption\"><span class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-credit\">Blink</span></figcaption></figure><p>Three cameras will set you back less than $40.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.popsci.com/gear/blink-security-camera-deals-amazon-early-black-friday-2023/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Save 60% on Blink Mini security cameras during Amazon&#8217;s early Black Friday sale</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.popsci.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Popular Science</a>.</p>", "link": "https://www.popsci.com/gear/blink-security-camera-deals-amazon-early-black-friday-2023", "date_published": "2023-10-26T12:55:00+00:00", "bookmarked": false, "dead": null, "artist": "Popular Science", "album": "Popular Science", "user": null, "language": "en-US", "thumbnail": "https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2021/04/28/cropped-PSC3.png?auto=webp&width=32&heigh